@startuml SignalReport - Sequenz Messungsablauf
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceFontSize 13
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1
skinparam roundcorner 10

actor Benutzer
participant SignalReportApp
participant Config
participant PingMeasurer
participant DnsMeasurer
participant HttpMeasurer
participant HostIdentifier
participant NetworkInfo
participant H2MeasurementRepository
database H2_Database as DB

Benutzer -> SignalReportApp : Starte Anwendung
SignalReportApp -> Config : load("config.json")
Config --> SignalReportApp : Config-Objekt
SignalReportApp -> H2MeasurementRepository : new H2MeasurementRepository()
H2MeasurementRepository -> DB : Verbinde / Erstelle Tabellen
DB --> H2MeasurementRepository : Verbindung hergestellt
SignalReportApp -> WebServer : start(port)
SignalReportApp -> HostIdentifier : getHostHash()
HostIdentifier --> SignalReportApp : "a3f8b2c1..."
SignalReportApp -> H2MeasurementRepository : registerHost(hash, hostname, os)
H2MeasurementRepository -> DB : INSERT INTO hosts

SignalReportApp -> SignalReportApp : Starte Mess-Schleife (alle X Sekunden)

loop Alle X Sekunden (konfigurierbar)
  SignalReportApp -> Config : getInstance()
  Config --> SignalReportApp : Aktuelle Config

  SignalReportApp -> Config : getMaintenanceWindow()
  Config --> SignalReportApp : MaintenanceWindow

  alt Maintenance-Fenster aktiv
    SignalReportApp -> SignalReportApp : Überspringe Messung
    SignalReportApp --> Benutzer : "⏸️ Maintenance-Fenster aktiv"
  else Normale Messung
    SignalReportApp -> Config : getTargets()
    Config --> SignalReportApp : ping="8.8.8.8", dns="google.com", http="https://example.com"

    SignalReportApp -> NetworkInfo : getExternalIPv4()
    NetworkInfo --> SignalReportApp : "85.182.xxx.xxx"

    SignalReportApp -> HostIdentifier : getHostHash()
    HostIdentifier --> SignalReportApp : "a3f8b2c1..."

    SignalReportApp -> H2MeasurementRepository : trackIpChange("85.182.xxx.xxx", "a3f8b2c1...")
    H2MeasurementRepository -> H2MeasurementRepository : getLastKnownIp("a3f8b2c1...")
    H2MeasurementRepository -> DB : SELECT new_ip FROM ip_changes WHERE host_hash = ?
    DB --> H2MeasurementRepository : "85.182.yyy.yyy"

    alt IP hat sich geändert
      H2MeasurementRepository -> H2MeasurementRepository : recordIpChange("85.182.yyy.yyy", "85.182.xxx.xxx", "CHANGE")
      H2MeasurementRepository -> DB : INSERT INTO ip_changes
      DB --> H2MeasurementRepository : Erfolg
    end

    SignalReportApp -> PingMeasurer : measure("8.8.8.8")
    PingMeasurer -> PingMeasurer : InetAddress.isReachable()
    PingMeasurer --> SignalReportApp : Measurement(latency=23.5, success=true)
    SignalReportApp -> H2MeasurementRepository : save(measurement)
    H2MeasurementRepository -> DB : INSERT INTO measurements

    SignalReportApp -> DnsMeasurer : measure("google.com")
    DnsMeasurer -> DnsMeasurer : InetAddress.getByName()
    DnsMeasurer --> SignalReportApp : Measurement(latency=12.3, success=true)
    SignalReportApp -> H2MeasurementRepository : save(measurement)
    H2MeasurementRepository -> DB : INSERT INTO measurements

    SignalReportApp -> HttpMeasurer : measure("https://example.com")
    HttpMeasurer -> HttpMeasurer : HttpClient.send()
    HttpMeasurer --> SignalReportApp : Measurement(latency=145.2, success=true)
    SignalReportApp -> H2MeasurementRepository : save(measurement)
    H2MeasurementRepository -> DB : INSERT INTO measurements

    SignalReportApp --> Benutzer : "✅ 3 Messungen gespeichert | IP: 85.182.xxx.xxx"
  end

  SignalReportApp -> SignalReportApp : Warte X Sekunden
end

note over SignalReportApp, DB
  Parallel dazu: Webserver läuft und
  beantwortet API-Anfragen von der UI
  (Live-Updates alle 5 Sekunden)
end note
@enduml